title: Testing - Psychometric

widgets.title: Summary Statistics
widgets.desc: This table displays aggregated figures on learner exam activity. Only completed exams are included in this analysis. P-Value refers to percentage of correct answers.

widgets.title: Confidence Levels on Questions
widgets.desc: This chart displays a summary of learner-marked confidence levels.

widgets.title: Exam Score Distribution
widgets.desc: This chart displays the frequency of exam score buckets. Only completed exams are included in this analysis.

widgets.title: Practice Question Statistics
widgets.desc:
This table shows how learners have performed on practice questions. It excludes instances in which learners took longer than fifteen minutes to answer a question.
P-Value refers to percentage of correct answers.

widgets.title: Distractor Analysis
widgets.desc:
This table displays various statistics for exam questions in the program.
Item difficulty is based on a question's elo rank relative to other questions on a given exam.

items.text: This dynamic dashboard presents timely data pertaining to exam- and item-level engagement — in aggregate, and at the Course level — scoped to the level of permission for your account.

widgets.title: Exam Performance
widgets.desc: This chart displays data on learner exam performance. Only completed exams are included in this analysis.
